Project Overview
This project analyzes transactional data from Bright Coffee Shop Sales to generate actionable 
insights that support business growth. The analysis was conducted in 
response to a new CEO’s strategic goal: increase revenue and improve product performance.
As a Junior Data Analyst, this project focuses on 
using SQL and data visualization techniques to uncover patterns in sales, 
customer behavior, and product performance.


Which products generate the most revenue?
What time of day does the store perform best?
What are the sales trends across products and time intervals?
What recommendations can improve overall sales performance?
